---
import DocsLayout from '../../layouts/DocsLayout.astro';
---

<DocsLayout title="Elements">
  <p>Elements are the building blocks of slides. Each element has a <code>type</code> and positioning properties.</p>

  <h2>Common Properties</h2>
  <p>All elements accept these positioning properties (in inches):</p>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Key</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>x</code></td><td>Horizontal position from left edge</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>y</code></td><td>Vertical position from top edge</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>w</code></td><td>Width</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>h</code></td><td>Height</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Text</h2>
  <pre><code class="language-yaml">- type: text
  x: 1
  y: 2
  w: 8
  h: 1.5
  text: "Hello, World!"
  size: 24
  font: $heading
  color: $primary
  bold: true
  italic: false
  align: center       # left, center, right
  valign: middle      # top, middle, bottom</code></pre>

  <h3>Bullets</h3>
  <pre><code class="language-yaml">- type: text
  x: 1
  y: 1.5
  w: 8
  h: 3
  size: 14
  bullets:
    - "First bullet point"
    - "Second bullet point"
    - &#123;text: "Bold bullet", bold: true, color: $accent&#125;</code></pre>

  <h3>Runs (Rich Text)</h3>
  <pre><code class="language-yaml">- type: text
  x: 1
  y: 2
  w: 4
  h: 2
  runs:
    - &#123;text: "$4.2M", size: 40, bold: true, color: $accent&#125;
    - &#123;text: "Revenue", size: 13, color: $muted&#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>Shape</h2>
  <pre><code class="language-yaml">- type: shape
  shape: rectangle    # rectangle, rounded, line, oval
  x: 0
  y: 0
  w: 10
  h: 0.06
  fill: $accent
  radius: 0.1        # for rounded rectangles
  shadow: soft        # default, soft, or omit
  line:
    color: $muted
    width: 1.5</code></pre>

  <h2>Group</h2>
  <p>Groups arrange items in row or grid layouts with automatic sizing:</p>

  <h3>Row Layout</h3>
  <pre><code class="language-yaml">- type: group
  layout: row
  x: 0.6
  y: 1.3
  w: 8.8
  h: 2.0
  gap: 0.3
  card:
    fill: $white
    radius: 0.1
    shadow: default
  items:
    - runs:
        - &#123;text: "$4.2M", size: 40, bold: true&#125;
        - &#123;text: "Revenue", size: 13, color: $muted&#125;
    - runs:
        - &#123;text: "89.3%", size: 40, bold: true&#125;
        - &#123;text: "Retention", size: 13, color: $muted&#125;</code></pre>

  <h3>Grid Layout</h3>
  <pre><code class="language-yaml">- type: group
  layout: grid
  columns: 3
  x: 0.6
  y: 1.2
  w: 8.8
  h: 4.0
  gap: 0.25
  card:
    fill: $white
    radius: 0.08
    border: "E0E4EA"
  items:
    - icon: &#123;name: gear, bg: $primary&#125;
      runs:
        - &#123;text: "Engineering", size: 14, bold: true&#125;
        - &#123;text: "47 features shipped", size: 11&#125;</code></pre>

  <h2>Group Properties</h2>
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr><th>Key</th><th>Description</th></tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr><td><code>layout</code></td><td><code>row</code> or <code>grid</code></td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>columns</code></td><td>Number of columns (grid only)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>gap</code></td><td>Space between items (inches)</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>card</code></td><td>Styling for each item's container</td></tr>
      <tr><td><code>items</code></td><td>Array of items (each can have <code>runs</code>, <code>icon</code>)</td></tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</DocsLayout>

<style>
  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin: 1rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  th, td {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 0.5rem 0.75rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  th {
    background: #f1f5f9;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
